{"tid":99962,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加拿大總理：歡迎難民到加拿大","createTime":"2017-01-29T15:18:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-09T19:27:49.000Z","uid":35790,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"239d3a394f72e76a40da88f10a66dc1cce26035e","tid":99962,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T15:18:31.000Z","msg":"加拿大高富帥總理：歡迎難民到加拿大<br />\n2017-01-29 20:11<br />\n<br />\n美國總統川普27日簽下暫時中止七個穆斯林國家人民入境的90天行政命令，對此，加拿大總理杜魯多（Justin Trudeau）在推特上發文表示反對。<br />\n<br />\n杜魯多推文寫道：「對那些逃離壓迫、恐怖與戰亂的人們，不論你們的信仰為何，加拿大民眾歡迎你們。多元化是我們的強項，歡迎到加拿大來。」<br />\n<br />\n杜魯多的推文，在短短幾小時內便獲得15萬人轉貼。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">加拿大在過去13個月收容近4萬名敘利亞難民，總理杜魯多因此受到全世界矚目</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n儘管杜魯多與川普的政治觀點差異很大，他至今仍克制對川普的批評。在近來幾次媒體談話中，杜魯多強調美、加之間的長期友誼，以及兩國的深厚經貿關係。美國是加拿大的最主要貿易夥伴。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">加拿大計劃在2017年增加30萬新移民，主要是經濟移民，但其中也包括4萬名難民</span>。<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/5/2257030\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F5%2F2257030&d=AMPtd42ADahZ7WU%2BVKQ9tXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=804f86ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/5/2257030</a>"},{"pid":"0136fe64f23d1b01c98c250929170b6ccb88253c","tid":99962,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T15:20:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d26434436edaaf01c852f94f06c232719ced022","tid":99962,"uid":61748,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T15:21:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a1ea4c1d5c81a15fc1812aaf4becb796a13dd931","tid":99962,"uid":4635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T15:21:51.000Z","msg":"準備過去加拿大了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"841f4c81e400a1db1d7a5113bf64fec6b95cd38a","tid":99962,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T15:28:54.000